Other Resources


Campus Film Office






UIC's urban campus is conveniently located within minutes of downtown Chicago and studio spaces. The UIC Campus Film Office will work with your production team to scout locations, coordinate the rental of spaces, administer contracts, schedule campus staff (e.g., security, carpenters, electricians), centrally bill for rentals and services, and oversee logistics to ensure that your film shoot is a success.
Not sure where you want to film on campus? Contact us at 312-996-5263 for a tour of campus. You can also check out videos of some popular filming locations below.
 






