            Filmed at UIC
          Heading link



 
Copy link



The following shows and movies have filmed on the UIC campus:

Feature film “Captive State”
“The Chi”
“Chicago Fire”
“Chicago Med”
“Chicago P.D.”
Netflix series “Easy”
Amazon series “Electric Dreams”
“Empire”
“Shameless”
“Sense8”
Indie film “Teacher”

The following companies have filmed commercials on campus:

Activia Yogurt
Quicken Loans
Samsung
Wendy’s

See a list of older movies and TV shows that have been filmed on campus.
 








